arStrings.szText: Entombed Legacy
Go with Donan to Astaroth's Tomb

I learned Donan and the other heroes did not kill Astaroth as the stories say, but imprisoned him in a soulstone buried beneath Eldhaime Keep. Lilith has also learned the location of the tomb. All we can do is follow and hope we are not too late to stop her from resurrecting Astaroth.
Follow Donan to the passage
I learned that Lilith has resurrected Astaroth by fusing his soulstone with Yorin. Shaken by the news, Donan has left the tomb. I should check on him.

Speak with Donan

Donan and I made our way through the blazing barracks only to discover Yorin's mace among one of those assigned to protect him. A previously hidden passage, blasted opened by some great force, has exposed a way down to Astaroth's tomb below. We must stop Lilith.
Escort Donan to Astaroth's tomb
Lilith already reached the tomb before us. This vast ancient druidic chamber once held the essence of Astaroth imprisoned in a soulstone, but Lilith has it now. And where is Yorin?
